<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.102.117067.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Tropicoporus cleistanthicola (MUBL 1089 holotype) A basidiomata (Holotype) B pore surface C cross-section of basidiome (arrows indicating stratified tube layers) D hymenial setae E-H basidiospores: E basidiospores in water F basidiospores in KOH G basidiospore in cotton blue H basidiospore in Melzer's reagent. Scale bars: 1 cm (A-C); 5 µm (D-H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/979924" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.102.117067.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Tropicoporus cleistanthicola (MUBL 1089 holotype) A contextual hyphae B tramal hyphae C hymenial setae D cystidioles E basidioles F basidia G basidiospores. Scale bars: 5 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/979925" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

